2.title: SAC tag config
2.code:
/*
 * Sets the mapping for the SAC (custom) tag - an object with key/value pairs.
 *
 * - if the value starts with a single '$' and that value is defined and
 *   populated in the b object when the tag fires, it will be filled with the
 *   value from the b object.
 * - otherwise, it will be treated as a simple string (the string will be used).
 */

b.sac_mapping_config = {
  cha: 'web',
  cat: '$page_category',
  category_full: '$page_category_full',
  cid: '$article_id',
  sit: '$site_cts_slug',
  country: '$site_country',
  site_name: '$site_name',
  page_id: '$page_id',
  page_type: '$page_type',

  event_category: '$event_category',
  event_label: '$event_label',
  event_value: '$event_value',
  event_interaction: '$event_interaction',

  user_id_legacy: '$user_id_legacy',
  adblocker: '$ads_blocked',
  id: '$page_view_id',
  video_id: '$video_id',

  ecom_order_id: '$ecommerce_order_id',
  ecom_order_store: '$ecommerce_order_store',
  ecom_order_total: '$ecommerce_order_total',
  ecom_order_subtotal: '$ecommerce_order_subtotal',
  ecom_order_tax: '$ecommerce_order_tax',
  ecom_order_shipping: '$ecommerce_order_shipping',
  ecom_order_promocode: '$ecommerce_order_promocode',

  ecom_product_id: '$ecommerce_product_id',
  ecom_product_name: '$ecommerce_product_name',
  ecom_product_brand: '$ecommerce_product_brand',
  ecom_product_variant: '$ecommerce_product_variant',
  ecom_product_category: '$ecommerce_product_category',
  ecom_product_quantity: '$ecommerce_product_quantity',
  ecom_product_price: '$ecommerce_product_price',
  ecom_product_discount: '$ecommerce_product_discount',

  ecom_currency: '$currency',

  ecom_action: '$ecommerce_action',

  ecom_list: '$ecommerce_list',
  ecom_list_product_id: '$ecommerce_list_product_id',
  ecom_list_product_name: '$ecommerce_list_product_name',
  ecom_list_product_brand: '$ecommerce_list_product_brand',
  ecom_list_product_variant: '$ecommerce_list_product_variant',
  ecom_list_product_category: '$ecommerce_list_product_category',
  ecom_list_product_price: '$ecommerce_list_product_price',
  ecom_list_product_position: '$ecommerce_list_product_position',

  ecom_product_position: '$ecommerce_product_position',

  ecom_checkout_step: '$ecommerce_checkout_step',
  ecom_checkout_option: '$ecommerce_checkout_option',

  ecom_promotion_creative: '$ecommerce_promotion_creative',
  ecom_promotion_id: '$ecommerce_promotion_id',
  ecom_promotion_name: '$ecommerce_promotion_name',
  ecom_promotion_position: '$ecommerce_promotion_position',

  ecom_user_country: '$user_country'
};
